1
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:45,000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

2
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,440
But I can't resist temptation.

3
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,040
What kind of temptation?

4
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,760
If someone is dating in front of me,

5
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,320
I'll also want to date.

6
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:04,760
Who is dating? You watch too many idol dramas.

7
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,760
The people close to me.

8
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,960
Those around me.

9
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,240
Are you talking about me?

10
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:13,920
Kiddo.

11
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,560
Why are you so petty?

12
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:19,000
You can't stop others from dating just because you can't date.

13
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,160
Isn't it a provocation

14
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,280
to date in front of me?

15
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:26,320
Fine, let's say you're right.

16
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,840
I won't talk about the future for now.

17
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:31,120
But we're going to talk

18
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,240
about your old boyfriend

19
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,720
who told you to go to Yihe to meet him.

20
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:37,920
It's quite a coincidence

21
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:40,160
because I'm from Yihe.

22
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:43,600
So if I ever find out

23
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:46,120
that you went to see him while you're still a minor,

24
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,360
then I'm afraid

25
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:54,120
you won't live to become an adult.

26
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,040
Let's begin the lesson.

27
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,040
How was the last exam?

28
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,600
Take point M as the intersection on side AB.

29
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,520
I explained it before. Like this problem.

30
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,360
Then try to recall the formula.

31
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,960
I'll explain static electricity first.

32
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,960
You got this problem correct.

33
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,360
This problem.

34
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:01,120
I was originally going to choose C.

35
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,320
C, you say?

36
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,160
I meant D.

37
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,480
D is the answer to this problem.

38
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,280
Pay more attention next time.

39
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,959
One incorrect multiple-choice problem.

40
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,280
You got 97 points.

41
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,200
Not bad.

42
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,280
You've improved a lot.

43
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:30,120
So,

44
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,880
you have no problem with physics now.

45
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:35,040
I won't come to tutor you anymore.

46
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,480
If there is anything you don't understand,

47
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,640
you can ask your brother

48
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,640
or your teacher.
You can ask me too.

49
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,360
Just send me a picture of what you don't understand.

50
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,840
I'll reply after I go through it.

51
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,080
My phone was confiscated.

52
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,520
Your brother will talk to your parents.

53
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,480
Don't worry.

54
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,000
Cheer up.

55
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,800
You've improved so much now.

56
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,720
So did I teach well?

57
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:11,920
All right then.

58
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,440
So will you have more exams after school starts?

59
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,920
Yes.

60
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:19,480
Then send me each exam's result.

61
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,480
You had better get high scores.

62
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,040
As long as there's an improvement,

63
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,520
I'll give you a gift.

64
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:32,920
Let's stop here for today.

65
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:52,480
HAPPY LUNAR NEW YEAR

66
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,480
Are you doing housework?

67
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,720
Is the lesson over?

68
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,360
-Yes. -Come and have some fruit.

69
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:05,120
-Thank you, Mrs. Sang. -Have some fruit.

70
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,400
I was just talking to my husband.

71
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,280
Let's celebrate Lunar New Year's Eve together.

72
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,240
Come and join us.

73
00:06:12,320 --> 00:06:13,520
Thank you for inviting me.

74
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:16,360
But I think I'll stay on campus.

75
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,960
It's amazing at school now.

76
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,160
They host a holiday dinner

77
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,280
and give us red packets.

78
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,480
Don't go back.

79
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,000
It will be boring being alone.

80
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,640
In that case,

81
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,680
all right then.

82
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,760
Let me help you, Mr. Sang.

83
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,200
Okay. Sang Zhi, pass that to me.

84
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,200
This one.

85
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,160
Let's stick it here.

86
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:37,640
This one needs to be upside down.

87
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,160
Is this one good, dear?

88
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,280
Should it be bigger?

89
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,000
If I give him a red packet,

90
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,920
it will seem a bit strange.

91
00:06:58,800 --> 00:07:00,240
He definitely won't accept it.

92
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,000
Jiaxu,

93
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,920
Happy Lunar New Year.

94
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,560
PROSPERITY

95
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,240
Sang Yan said

96
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,280
you'll stay in Nanwu after graduation.

97
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,400
Have you found a job?

98
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:14,160
Yes, I plan to work at the game company

99
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,360
where I interned.

100
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,000
That's great.

101
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,520
Keep it up.

102
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,560
Okay, let's put it up.

103
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,160
Allow me.

104
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,320
Having it up there will be good.

105
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:25,600
At the top.

106
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,720
-A bit higher. -Higher.

107
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:29,080
-Zhizhi. -Perfect. All right.

108
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,600
Help me clear the table.

109
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,600
Right here.

110
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,320
Stop sweeping already.

111
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:36,159
Wash the rag and wipe the table.

112
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,120
Okay.

113
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,600
-It's all done. -Okay, thank you.

114
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,200
Of course.

115
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,200
GOOD FORTUNE

116
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:40,560
GOOD FORTUNE

117
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:41,560
How does it look?

118
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,400
Okay.

119
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,560
-That's enough. -So little?

120
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,920
That's enough for me. Thank you.

121
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,160
Okay. It's time to toast.

122
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,400
Happy Lunar New Year!

123
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:05,680
-Happy Lunar New Year! -Happy Lunar New Year!

124
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:07,240
-Dear, Happy Lunar New Year. -Cheers.

125
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,000
I dare you to finish all of this.

126
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:10,920
-Cheers. -Go away!

127
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,880
-He won't clink glasses. -It's such a big bottle.

128
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,120
The most exciting part

129
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,840
is yet to come.

130
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,400
Dear, you'll be the first to get this.

131
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:24,960
Do I get a red packet too?

132
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,080
Perfect.

133
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:28,640
Thank you, dear.

134
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,960
I love you.

135
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:36,360
-Dad and Mom, Happy New Year! -Dad and Mom, Happy New Year!

136
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,760
-May your wishes come true! -May your wishes come true!

137
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,080
-Be happy… -Stay healthy…

138
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,520
"Be happy" comes first.

139
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,440
It's "stay healthy".

140
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:43,560
No, it's "be happy"!

141
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:44,840
Fine.

142
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,600
-Be happy every day! -Be happy every day!

143
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,960
-Stay healthy! -Stay healthy!

144
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:50,640
-I like it. -Good. Here you go, Sang Yan.

145
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,000
Thank you, Dad.

146
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,480
Sang Zhi, this is yours.

147
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,560
Thank you, Dad.

148
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:58,040
-Dad. -Thank you, Mom.

149
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,800
You're being so unfair.

150
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:01,760
You're almost a university graduate.

151
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,160
You're lucky to even receive one.

152
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,600
Sang Zhi.

153
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:07,560
What should you do after getting your phone?

154
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:10,480
I'll uninstall the games.

155
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:11,400
What else?

156
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,760
What about your online dating prospect?

157
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,840
I already deleted it long ago.

158
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,640
What about his phone number?

159
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,560
I don't have his number.

160
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:26,200
Online dating doesn't use phone numbers.

161
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:27,440
I'm telling the truth.

162
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:30,280
Really?

163
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:33,080
You can see for yourself.

164
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:36,760
You don't even have enough money

165
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,400
to afford game currency.

166
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,600
-Why are you dating online? -Stop talking already.

167
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:42,760
-All right. -Cut it out. Stop arguing.

168
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:44,680
-Let's eat. -Eat up.

169
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:46,560
I have something to say before we eat.

170
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,560
I hope

171
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:50,880
my two lovely children will grow up

172
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:53,320
and behave a bit more

173
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:55,120
in this new year.

174
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,480
And you.

175
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:57,840
-Be more mature. -He means you.

176
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,360
-All right, let's eat. -Okay, let's dig in.

177
00:12:04,880 --> 00:12:06,320
By the way, Zhizhi.

178
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:08,200
Didn't you want

179
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,760
to buy a set of anime merchandise?

180
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,960
Now that your brother has money,

181
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:13,280
ask him to buy it for you.

182
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,680
Why should I? No way.

183
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,480
Thank you, Sang Yan. Thank you.

184
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,680
Sang Yan is the most generous.

185
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,480
Sang Yan, have some of this.

186
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,600
A toast to Sang Yan.

187
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:30,360
-Happy New Year. -Happy New Year.

188
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:33,000
This is for you.

189
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:36,480
At least you have a conscience.

190
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,440
-But it's not much. -You like eating this.

191
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,600
-It's delicious. -Really?

192
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:44,880
I want this one.

193
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,760
JIAXU

194
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,640
It's from Jiaxu.

195
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:03,080
Sang Yan, you did well. Have more.

196
00:13:03,160 --> 00:13:04,640
-Thank you, Mom. -Should we go on a trip?

197
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:07,480
Sang Zhi, I wish you happiness every day

198
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:08,800
and find your dreams soon.

199
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:09,920
Happy Lunar New Year.

200
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,920
-Sure. -Zhizhi.

201
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:14,360
How about going skiing in a few days?

202
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:17,160
Skiing? Sure.

203
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:19,440
Okay, then make up an itinerary for us.

204
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,440
-Okay. -It's busy during the holidays.

205
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:22,760
-So book early. -That's right.

206
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,480
-Next to number three. -Forget about numbers.

207
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:32,760
How about salt with vinegar?

208
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,680
-Footsteps. -Listen to my upper couplet.

209
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:36,040
It starts with "Perfectly."

210
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,560
-Damn. -"Perfectly matched."

211
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,920
-What matched? -Behind the bridge.

212
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:41,400
Perfectly matched, matched as in paired.

213
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,400
That's a good start.

214
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,920
I follow that with Minister.

215
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,440
-Move. -Minister against Cannon.

216
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,840
Why is it Minister against Cannon?

217
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:51,440
You move the Minister, and I counter with the Cannon.

218
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,840
It's Chinese chess. Get it?

219
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:55,240
I'll put it this way.

220
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:57,160
I structured these five characters together.

221
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,720
Thank you, Jiaxu.

222
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:06,080
Happy Lunar New Year.

223
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:21,960
YIHE CITY NURSING HOME

224
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:33,680
ANSWER

225
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:34,800
YIHE CITY NURSING HOME

226
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:37,840
Hello?

227
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,840
Hello. Are you Mr. Duan Jiaxu?

228
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:41,080
Yes.

229
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:44,320
Your dad has severe pulmonary edema caused by a lung infection

230
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:46,280
and must be transferred immediately for drainage.

231
00:14:48,080 --> 00:14:49,680
The current condition is quite urgent.

232
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:52,320
Please come as soon as possible to sign the consent form.

233
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,760
Okay, I understand. Thank you.

234
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:29,320
CHAPTER SIX, DISTANCE

235
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:31,320
WHEN YOU ARE IN ANOTHER CITY

236
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:35,400
Mr. Sang, your package.

237
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:36,320
Okay, thank you.

238
00:15:42,800 --> 00:15:43,640
Hey, silly dog.

239
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:47,920
It has a name. It's Winner.

240
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,400
Silly dog, come here.

241
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,240
Come here. Let me tell you.

242
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,320
Come here.

243
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:55,080
Listen. Look.

244
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:58,000
You look so similar to him.

245
00:15:58,080 --> 00:15:59,640
You two look exactly alike.

246
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:10,480
Wait right there.

247
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,000
Duan Jiaxu sent this to you.

248
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:14,760
It's your reward for ranking 20th

249
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,080
in the placement test

250
00:16:16,160 --> 00:16:17,680
and scoring 95 on the physics exam.

251
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:22,080
Why didn't he give it to me himself?

252
00:16:22,160 --> 00:16:23,000
Didn't he tell you?

253
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:24,320
He went back to his hometown.

254
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:25,920
He's back in Yihe.

255
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,720
He said something came up at home.

256
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:30,120
Why don't you ask him yourself?

257
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,200
Wait.

258
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:38,200
Then will he come back for the graduation ceremony?

259
00:16:38,760 --> 00:16:40,200
Of course he will.

260
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:46,520
Why did he leave without saying goodbye?

261
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:08,160
XURI MIDDLE-HIGH SCHOOL TO NANWU UNIVERSITY

262
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:13,079
2 HOURS AND 33 MINUTES

263
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:19,160
Sang Yan, are you coming home today?

264
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:30,840
SILLY DOG

265
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,280
What does this mean?

266
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:36,600
Why are you taking your time when class is over?

267
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:39,480
My sister is probably in trouble again.

268
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:41,040
She asked if I'm going home.

269
00:17:41,120 --> 00:17:42,280
Is she in trouble again?

270
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:03,720
It was awesome just now,

271
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:05,720
tossing the basketball with this pose.

272
00:18:05,800 --> 00:18:07,840
I was off my game today.

273
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:13,920
Hello?

274
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:15,960
Sang Yan, it's already Friday.

275
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:17,120
Why aren't you coming home?

276
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,560
There's a BOGO promotion on candy

277
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:20,880
at the convenience store today.

278
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:23,040
I bought an extra pack. I can share it with you.

279
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,400
If I want candy, I can buy it myself.

280
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,320
Just tell me what you want.

281
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:30,200
Nothing. I'm just asking.

282
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:32,640
Well, I can just not go home.

283
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,040
-Right? -It was cheap.

284
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:35,880
-You can invite friends over. -Duan Jiaxu!

285
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:39,560
Where are you going?

286
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,680
Where are you guys going?

287
00:18:40,760 --> 00:18:41,760
I'm going home for a bit.

288
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:44,240
I happen to be going to your area.

289
00:18:44,320 --> 00:18:45,320
Let's go together.

290
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:47,680
Sure. Come over for dinner if you're free.

291
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:48,600
Okay.

292
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:51,040
I'm not joining you.

293
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:52,400
I'm going back to the dorm.

294
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,480
-Okay. -Bye.

295
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:54,520
Bye.

296
00:18:54,600 --> 00:18:56,560
-Hello, little demon. -Suspicious.

297
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:58,240
What's wrong?

298
00:18:58,760 --> 00:18:59,600
She hung up on me.
Let's go.

299
00:19:23,840 --> 00:19:25,360
Why don't I call Sang Yan

300
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,000
and ask where they are?

301
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:35,320
Forget it.

302
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,280
They should be here soon.

303
00:19:40,600 --> 00:19:42,480
Don't worry. What's the situation?

304
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:49,040
-Again, Chen Junwen? -He's finally home!

305
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:51,960
How many times have you forgotten your keys?

306
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:54,840
I can't bring it to you.

307
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,080
You come to get it yourself.

308
00:19:58,520 --> 00:20:00,400
Did you forget to bring your brain too?

309
00:20:00,480 --> 00:20:02,280
I'm already home. How can I open it for you?

310
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,000
Why is he alone?

311
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:08,400
Little demon!

312
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:10,880
Why didn't you close the door?

313
00:20:10,960 --> 00:20:12,000
There are mosquitoes!

314
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:14,720
Duan Jiaxu was supposed to come with me,

315
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:16,280
but the library gave him a call,

316
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:17,520
so he had to go back to work.

317
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:19,720
As you know, he's crazy about making money.

318
00:20:21,040 --> 00:20:22,440
All right, that's all.

319
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:23,400
I'm hanging up now.

320
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:25,360
Bye.

321
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:27,160
Little demon.

322
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:29,920
Why did you want me home?

323
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,400
Dad and Mom wanted

324
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:35,080
to have dinner together this weekend.

325
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:37,000
Have dinner together?

326
00:20:38,960 --> 00:20:40,880
Couldn't you tell me over the phone?

327
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:44,160
Dad! Mom!

328
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:45,760
Sang Yan? Sang Yan is back.

329
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:48,320
I thought you were coming home tomorrow.

330
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:54,320
Let's have dinner together this weekend.

331
00:20:55,840 --> 00:20:57,040
You're getting more thoughtful.

332
00:20:58,240 --> 00:21:00,000
We're sweaty from a day of work.

333
00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:00,920
We'll shower first.
-Okay. -Okay.

334
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:03,040
Afterward, I'll make dinner.

335
00:21:03,120 --> 00:21:04,240
Okay.

336
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:06,720
Mom, why not let Sang Yan make dinner?

337
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:08,120
Let him make dinner?

338
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,280
That would work too.

339
00:21:09,360 --> 00:21:10,560
Cook the rice first.

340
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:11,800
Wash the vegetables too.

341
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,480
Cooking rice is too simple.

342
00:21:13,560 --> 00:21:15,320
It's okay. Let him cook the rice.

343
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,360
I'll cook the rest.

344
00:21:29,280 --> 00:21:30,240
Sang Yan.

345
00:21:30,320 --> 00:21:32,480
Which library is Jiaxu working at?

346
00:21:32,560 --> 00:21:33,960
Is it the university's library?

347
00:21:36,560 --> 00:21:37,680
Why are you asking me this?

348
00:21:38,760 --> 00:21:40,600
Nothing. I'm just curious.

349
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:42,360
Are all university students so busy?

350
00:21:43,280 --> 00:21:44,920
What are you usually busy with?

351
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:47,600
I'm busy trying to get away from a little demon like you.

352
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:49,520
Busy sleeping in class.

353
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,920
Isn't that the same as middle school students?

354
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,920
How can it be the same?

355
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:58,040
University students have one more thing to do,

356
00:21:58,120 --> 00:21:59,000
which is dating.

357
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:00,720
Dating?

358
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,720
Well, I should've known.

359
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:06,240
A kid like you wouldn't understand this.

360
00:22:06,320 --> 00:22:07,600
How is that possible?

361
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:09,200
Why would any girl like you?

362
00:22:10,360 --> 00:22:12,640
Listen, plenty of girls chase after me.

363
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:14,840
Not even a high-speed train can fit them all.

364
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,520
What's wrong with you?

365
00:22:19,160 --> 00:22:20,520
It has been so long

366
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:21,920
since I've heard anyone

367
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:23,880
tell such a tall tale.

368
00:22:24,880 --> 00:22:25,720
You don't believe me?

369
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:28,080
Okay, listen.

370
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:30,400
Do you know why

371
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:33,160
none of my roommates have girlfriends?

372
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:37,600
None of them have girlfriends?

373
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:39,360
It's because those girls

374
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:40,880
are lining up to pursue me.

375
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:43,160
Who would believe that nonsense?

376
00:22:58,280 --> 00:22:59,680
SENDER, DUAN JIAXU

377
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:04,200
Another reward from Jiaxu for my exam scores.

378
00:23:59,360 --> 00:24:00,200
Hello?

379
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:01,960
Hello, Jiaxu.

380
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:05,960
I received the package you sent.

381
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:08,120
It's a black dog plushie.

382
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:12,200
So? Do you like it?

383
00:24:14,280 --> 00:24:17,840
It looks a bit familiar to me.

384
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:18,920
Is that so?

385
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,600
Does it look like Sang Yan?

386
00:24:26,080 --> 00:24:27,920
You still remember my essay.

387
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:29,160
Of course I do.

388
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:31,920
I was walking on the street one day

389
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:33,240
and saw this dog.

390
00:24:34,240 --> 00:24:36,240
It reminded me of your drawing back then.

391
00:24:37,360 --> 00:24:38,800
So I thought

392
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:40,320
it would be a perfect gift for you.

393
00:24:40,840 --> 00:24:42,320
Congratulations on scoring 95 points

394
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,560
on the physics exam this time.

395
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:47,720
By the way, Jiaxu.

396
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,560
Give me your address.

397
00:24:50,280 --> 00:24:51,680
I want to send you something.

398
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:54,080
Do you want to send me something?

399
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,640
I'm just exchanging favors.

400
00:24:58,600 --> 00:24:59,560
No need.

401
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:02,200
Why? It's important.

402
00:25:03,320 --> 00:25:05,160
What is your monthly allowance?

403
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:07,320
Keep the money

404
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:08,840
and spend it on yourself, okay?

405
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:10,160
No need to send me any gifts.

406
00:25:10,760 --> 00:25:11,920
Let me send you something.

407
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:14,400
You really don't have to.

408
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:15,640
The fact that you want to

409
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:17,240
already makes me happy.

410
00:25:19,200 --> 00:25:21,920
So Sang Yan said

411
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:25,240
you will come back for your graduation ceremony.

412
00:25:25,320 --> 00:25:26,160
Is that true?

413
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:27,360
Yes.

414
00:25:27,840 --> 00:25:28,920
Will you be going?

415
00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:31,320
Yes.

416
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:33,080
That's great.

417
00:25:33,160 --> 00:25:34,480
We'll see each other then.

418
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,000
I have to go now.

419
00:25:38,760 --> 00:25:39,600
Bye.

420
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:41,040
Bye.

421
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,600
Then consider it your graduation gift.

422
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,680
Who's there?

423
00:26:21,480 --> 00:26:22,560
It has been a long time.

424
00:26:25,520 --> 00:26:26,560
Why are you here?

425
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:30,080
Aren't you inviting me in?

426
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:33,560
It's not a good time.

427
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:35,200
Sorry about that.

428
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:42,240
Here.

429
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:46,280
Isn't that person in a bad condition?

430
00:26:46,760 --> 00:26:47,960
Don't worry

431
00:26:48,040 --> 00:26:49,480
about returning the money this month.

432
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:51,800
It's fine.

433
00:26:52,280 --> 00:26:53,440
I can figure it out myself.

434
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:56,440
I just don't want you to have a hard time.

435
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:58,320
It's really not necessary. Thank you.

436
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:02,760
By the way,

437
00:27:02,840 --> 00:27:05,280
has the time for your graduation ceremony been set yet?

438
00:27:05,360 --> 00:27:06,880
Can I go too?

439
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:11,480
No need.

440
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:19,600
It's all right.

441
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:21,200
Since you're returning to Yihe,

442
00:27:21,280 --> 00:27:22,920
we'll get a chance to meet up.

443
00:27:24,040 --> 00:27:25,480
Then

444
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:27,480
I wish you an early happy graduation.

445
00:27:27,560 --> 00:27:28,680
Thank you.

446
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:31,920
I'll be in touch.

447
00:27:59,360 --> 00:28:01,080
-Three, two, one! -Three, two, one!

448
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,760
-Cheese! -Cheese!

449
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:04,160
Smile a little.

450
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,120
A bit lower.

451
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:07,160
Okay, smile.

452
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:09,320
-Three, two, one. -Hi, Sang Yan.

453
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,520
Your classmate?

454
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:11,680
Actually, I don't know him.

455
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:13,120
-Sang Yan! -Sang Yan, come here!

456
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,120
Over there.

457
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:24,520
-Hello, Mr. Sang. -Hello, Mr. Sang.

458
00:28:24,600 --> 00:28:25,760
Congratulations on graduating.

459
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:28,000
Thank you, Mr. Sang.

460
00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:33,680
Mr. Sang, where is Mrs. Sang?

461
00:28:33,760 --> 00:28:36,560
She's sick with a cold and fever.

462
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:37,880
I told her to rest at home.

463
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:40,240
-Many people have fallen sick lately. -Yes.

464
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:41,280
Sang Yan, you're late.

465
00:28:41,360 --> 00:28:42,920
We need to take a picture together.

466
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:44,400
Okay, come on.

467
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:46,720
-Let me help you take it. -Thank you, Mr. Sang.

468
00:28:46,800 --> 00:28:47,800
No problem.

469
00:28:49,360 --> 00:28:50,520
Look this way.

470
00:28:50,600 --> 00:28:53,120
One, two, three.

471
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,200
Make a different pose.

472
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:57,760
Ready? One, two, three.

473
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:59,080
It's all done. Take a look.

474
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:01,440
-Thank you, Mr. Sang. -Qian Fei!

475
00:29:02,520 --> 00:29:04,040
-Take pictures with us! -Come, Qian Fei!

476
00:29:04,120 --> 00:29:04,960
-Come on! -Let's go.

477
00:29:05,040 --> 00:29:06,360
-Come! -Dad, I'm going over there.

478
00:29:06,440 --> 00:29:07,640
Jiaxu, come and join us.

479
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:08,600
-Come! -I'm coming!

480
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:10,720
I heard you'll work in your hometown.

481
00:29:11,200 --> 00:29:13,240
Yes. I've already found a job.

482
00:29:14,360 --> 00:29:15,840
That's not a bad idea either.

483
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:17,560
After all, you're familiar with the area.

484
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:20,080
If you ever visit Nanwu,

485
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:21,360
come to my house for a meal.

486
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:22,640
Okay, that's for sure.

487
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:23,680
Good.

488
00:29:23,760 --> 00:29:25,560
Let's go take a photo with your brother.

489
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:26,880
-Let's take it together. -Okay.

490
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:31,760
It has been a long time, Sang Zhi.

491
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:38,320
This is for you.

492
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:40,520
For me?

493
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:44,400
I thought it was for your brother.

494
00:29:45,480 --> 00:29:47,400
He already has one.

495
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:50,520
This one is for my physics tutor.

496
00:29:51,280 --> 00:29:52,400
I wish you

497
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:53,680
a happy graduation

498
00:29:53,760 --> 00:29:54,760
and happiness every day.

499
00:29:56,040 --> 00:29:56,880
Thank you.

500
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:58,600
I like it very much.

501
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:02,160
Then I wish my student

502
00:30:02,240 --> 00:30:03,400
a bright future

503
00:30:03,480 --> 00:30:04,640
and smooth academic progress.

504
00:30:06,840 --> 00:30:08,880
The graduation ceremony is about to begin.

505
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:10,080
All graduating students,

506
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:11,680
please gather in the auditorium.

507
00:30:13,560 --> 00:30:14,920
Jiaxu, you should go ahead.

508
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:16,960
I'll go and find my brother by myself.

509
00:30:17,520 --> 00:30:18,880
It's okay. I'll take you there.

510
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:20,120
I'll text your brother.

511
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:23,240
Come on.

512
00:30:34,120 --> 00:30:35,360
-Jiaxu. -Jiaxu.

513
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,880
-Hey, Jiaxu. -Come and join us.

514
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:38,280
-Come take a picture. -Okay.

515
00:30:38,360 --> 00:30:39,880
I'll take a picture with them.

516
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:41,280
Jiaxu, who is this?

517
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,840
My sister.

518
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,920
Hi. Can you help us take a photo?

519
00:30:46,520 --> 00:30:47,360
Sure.

520
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:49,880
-Thank you. Just press this. -Okay.

521
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:50,800
Come on, everyone.

522
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:51,920
-Come on. -Picture time.

523
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:52,880
-Okay. -This is it.

524
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:54,280
-Stand there. -Okay.

525
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:55,280
Okay.

526
00:30:55,360 --> 00:30:56,360
Three.

527
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,640
Two.

528
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:58,560
One.

529
00:30:59,760 --> 00:31:00,680
Good.
Okay, thank you.

530
00:31:01,760 --> 00:31:03,440
-Jiaxu. -It's a great picture.

531
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:05,680
Professor Zhang, thank you for your help.

532
00:31:05,760 --> 00:31:07,680
I hope to see you shine and excel

533
00:31:07,760 --> 00:31:10,880
in the gaming industry.

534
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:12,680
-I'll do my best. -I believe in you.

535
00:31:12,760 --> 00:31:13,640
Thank you.

536
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:15,560
Okay, I'm going inside first.

537
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:16,840
-Okay. -Okay, Professor.

538
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:18,400
Jiaxu.

539
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:21,880
Participating in competitions and research projects with you

540
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,760
was the most painful and happiest thing for me

541
00:31:23,840 --> 00:31:25,200
in these four years.

542
00:31:25,280 --> 00:31:26,480
Both painful and happy?

543
00:31:26,560 --> 00:31:28,280
-Yes. -It sounds complicated.

544
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:29,680
Do you remember

545
00:31:29,760 --> 00:31:31,200
when we stayed up late every night?

546
00:31:31,280 --> 00:31:33,120
-Seriously. -We could only eat instant noodles.

547
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,840
Those were hard times.

548
00:31:34,920 --> 00:31:35,920
But it will all pay off.

549
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,320
I'll be returning to my hometown tomorrow.

550
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:39,520
Are you leaving tomorrow?

551
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:43,680
-What about you two? -I'll probably leave tomorrow too.

552
00:31:43,760 --> 00:31:45,680
I wonder if we'll see each other again.

553
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:47,240
It's okay.

554
00:31:47,320 --> 00:31:48,760
We will get a chance to meet again.

555
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:50,960
I'm heading inside.

556
00:31:51,040 --> 00:31:52,320
-Okay. -Okay, I'll see you later.

557
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:01,720
Jiaxu.

558
00:32:04,360 --> 00:32:06,320
Does that mean it'll be difficult

559
00:32:06,400 --> 00:32:09,680
to see your classmates after graduation?

560
00:32:09,760 --> 00:32:10,800
Two, one.

561
00:32:10,880 --> 00:32:12,040
I guess so.

562
00:32:12,960 --> 00:32:14,200
How do I explain this to you?

563
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:17,440
We majored in the same discipline,

564
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,360
but after we enter society,

565
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:22,080
everyone will make their own choice.

566
00:32:23,360 --> 00:32:25,800
Gradually, we'll take different paths.

567
00:32:26,560 --> 00:32:27,520
It could be

568
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:30,800
that it will be really hard to meet again.

569
00:32:39,800 --> 00:32:42,000
Then what about me?

570
00:32:42,560 --> 00:32:43,440
You?

571
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:48,280
You're not the same as them.

572
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:52,720
They won't be like my dear sister

573
00:32:53,360 --> 00:32:54,880
who snuck me a red packet

574
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:56,440
during Lunar New Year

575
00:32:59,760 --> 00:33:01,000
and even came to give me flowers

576
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,080
on my graduation day.

577
00:33:09,480 --> 00:33:10,680
Don't worry.

578
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,440
After I leave,

579
00:33:12,520 --> 00:33:14,240
I'll come back to see you whenever I'm free.

580
00:33:15,760 --> 00:33:18,320
When will you be free?

581
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:22,080
I'll let you know in advance

582
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:23,000
before I come back.

583
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:24,640
Okay?

584
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:34,680
Xiaozhou, can you do me a favor?

585
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:35,960
Sure.

586
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:40,200
Help me take a photo with my sister.

587
00:33:40,280 --> 00:33:41,400
Okay.

588
00:33:43,360 --> 00:33:44,320
Hold this.

589
00:33:46,080 --> 00:33:46,960
Come on.

590
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,840
Both of you look at the camera.

591
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:53,840
Okay, smile a bit more.

592
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:11,920
-Happy graduation! -Happy graduation!

593
00:34:16,239 --> 00:34:17,639
Enough. Don't drink too much.

594
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:19,760
You can't hold your alcohol,

595
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,199
so don't drink too much.

596
00:34:21,280 --> 00:34:22,800
We're celebrating today.

597
00:34:23,560 --> 00:34:24,880
You two are inseparable again.

598
00:34:24,960 --> 00:34:26,840
I have to get to the bottom of this today.

599
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,320
You two always stick together

600
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:29,600
and never find a girlfriend.

601
00:34:30,600 --> 00:34:31,960
I understand if it's Sang Yan.

602
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:33,199
With his temper,

603
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,440
who would like him?

604
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:36,480
Shut up.

605
00:34:36,560 --> 00:34:37,719
Jiaxu, what about you?

606
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:39,360
Yes. Why don't you have a girlfriend?

607
00:34:41,040 --> 00:34:41,920
What do we say?

608
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,239
See?

609
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,159
That's why we're best buds.

610
00:34:48,239 --> 00:34:49,360
What? Is there a problem?

611
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,240
Duan Jiaxu!

612
00:34:57,880 --> 00:35:00,000
I thought I was your best friend!

613
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,880
How could you have a change of heart?

614
00:35:02,960 --> 00:35:04,720
You are. Of course you are.

615
00:35:04,800 --> 00:35:06,360
Let him be. He's such a crybaby.

616
00:35:06,440 --> 00:35:08,160
-He's ignoring me. -It's okay.

617
00:35:08,240 --> 00:35:09,480
I'll take care of you. Come.

618
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:10,520
Are you really crying?

619
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:12,000
How can you cry for real?

620
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:13,080
You're a grown-up!

621
00:35:14,080 --> 00:35:15,360
Can someone open a bottle for me?

622
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,600
Give it to me.

623
00:35:16,680 --> 00:35:17,600
Thank you.

624
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:20,480
Jiaxu, come and have a drink.

625
00:35:20,560 --> 00:35:21,640
-Cheers! -Cheers, guys.

626
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:22,640
Happy graduation.

627
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:24,640
We've graduated, and you're drinking cola?

628
00:35:24,720 --> 00:35:26,160
-Drink beer. -I can't drink alcohol.

629
00:35:26,240 --> 00:35:27,120
No way.

630
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:28,880
You're spoiling the fun. Come on.

631
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,000
Give it to me.

632
00:35:30,080 --> 00:35:31,040
Okay, cheers!

633
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:32,040
Come on, guys.
There they go again.

634
00:35:33,040 --> 00:35:34,320
Are you drinking on his behalf?

635
00:35:34,920 --> 00:35:36,440
Stop wasting time and drink up.

636
00:35:36,520 --> 00:35:37,360
-Drink up! -Cheers!

637
00:35:37,440 --> 00:35:39,600
-Cheers! -Cheers!

638
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:40,640
Jiaxu, drink up.

639
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:59,200
Don't stop drinking. Finish it.

640
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:00,720
Is it for the whales or the sharks?

641
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:02,520
I can finish it. I'll drink first.

642
00:36:02,600 --> 00:36:04,120
Listen. Wait a moment.

643
00:36:04,200 --> 00:36:05,280
I want to ask you something.

644
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:06,880
-I'll ask you first. -No, I'll ask you.

645
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:08,760
-Do you have a crush on her? -Me?

646
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:11,000
Do you have a crush on her?

647
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:12,120
Do you?

648
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:13,400
Let me finish this drink first.

649
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:15,720
Today is the last day.

650
00:36:15,800 --> 00:36:16,880
It's the last day, right?

651
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:17,880
It's the last day.

652
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:20,280
If you don't tell the truth, you won't get another chance.

653
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:21,240
JIANG YING

654
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:23,200
I'm happy you're coming back to Yihe.

655
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:24,440
Happy graduation.

656
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:26,440
CALL CANCELED

657
00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:28,920
I'M HAPPY YOU'RE COMING BACK TO YIHE. HAPPY GRADUATION.

658
00:36:33,720 --> 00:36:34,960
-What's wrong? -Jiaxu.

659
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:36,600
I can't bear to part with you.

660
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:39,920
Are you drunk?

661
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:40,840
No.

662
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:42,680
Why are you alone?
He's drunk.

663
00:36:44,400 --> 00:36:45,600
I'm not.

664
00:36:45,680 --> 00:36:47,080
You are. Stop denying it.

665
00:36:47,160 --> 00:36:48,520
Come. Let's drink.

666
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,920
-Who turned Qian Fei into this? -Come on, drink.

667
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:53,200
Come and drink. Qian Fei, here.

668
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:55,160
-Don't drink with him. -This is our last time.

669
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:04,640
-Here. -Happy graduation, guys!

670
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:06,280
-Cheers. -Drink up.

671
00:37:32,160 --> 00:37:33,520
You drank too much.

672
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:36,800
Jiaxu, I want to ask you something.

673
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:38,760
When I'm no longer around,

674
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,840
who will watch over you?

675
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,440
Don't worry.

676
00:37:42,520 --> 00:37:44,360
Many people are eyeing me.

677
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:50,240
Duan Jiaxu.

678
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,600
You and Chen Junwen are going back home.

679
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:55,320
Only Sang Yan and I will be in Nanwu.

680
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:57,880
I don't know what is good about Yihe.

681
00:37:57,960 --> 00:37:59,000
Why do you have to go back?

682
00:38:00,280 --> 00:38:01,560
Enough. Let's keep drinking.

683
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:04,040
You were so loud earlier.

684
00:38:04,120 --> 00:38:05,200
Look at you now.

685
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:06,880
You're right.

686
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:14,360
You're home.

687
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:16,600
Jiaxu.

688
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:20,080
Will you be okay in Yihe?

689
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:24,360
Promise me you'll live well in Yihe.

690
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:26,400
Of course, I'll be fine.

691
00:38:28,720 --> 00:38:29,560
Sit.

692
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:31,360
Jiaxu.

693
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:34,520
You must come and visit us regularly.

694
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,200
I'll come back often.

695
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,160
Sang Yan.

696
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:43,280
Are you home?

697
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:45,280
-Mr. and Mrs. Sang. -Xiaoduan, you're here too.

698
00:38:45,360 --> 00:38:47,080
What's wrong? Did he drink too much?

699
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:48,600
We celebrated our graduation.

700
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:52,120
-Why did he drink so much? -Thank you for bringing him home.

701
00:38:52,200 --> 00:38:53,040
Give him some water.

702
00:38:53,120 --> 00:38:54,800
-Okay. -I'll make hangover soup for him.

703
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:55,720
Okay.

704
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,600
Why did he push himself to drink so much?

705
00:38:57,680 --> 00:38:59,320
Sang Yan, have some water.

706
00:39:01,120 --> 00:39:02,880
-Move slowly. -I'm going to go, Mrs. Sang.

707
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:05,280
Wait. Where are you spending the night?

708
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:07,680
There's an inn nearby.

709
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:10,640
Don't waste money. Just sleep in Sang Yan's room.

710
00:39:10,720 --> 00:39:11,760
Don't go to the trouble.

711
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:13,120
Not at all.

712
00:39:13,200 --> 00:39:14,520
Zhizhi, you're here too.

713
00:39:14,600 --> 00:39:15,800
Xiaoduan will spend the night.

714
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,760
Get him a new towel and toothbrush.

715
00:39:17,840 --> 00:39:19,720
It's really okay, Mrs. Sang. I can manage.

716
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:22,720
Stop turning me down. Go upstairs now.

717
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,360
It's all right.

718
00:39:26,040 --> 00:39:27,080
Are you feeling better now?

719
00:39:27,160 --> 00:39:28,920
-Thank you for having me. -It's no problem.

720
00:39:30,840 --> 00:39:31,880
Bring him upstairs.

721
00:39:32,520 --> 00:39:33,840
Are you feeling better now?

722
00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:42,320
Little rascal. Go on now.

723
00:39:42,400 --> 00:39:43,520
Okay, it's fine.

724
00:39:43,600 --> 00:39:45,040
Don't worry about it. I've got it.

725
00:39:45,120 --> 00:39:46,600
-Okay. -Zhizhi, bring him upstairs.

726
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,840
Why did you drink so much?

727
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:56,320
Dear, is the soup ready?

728
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,080
Just wait a little longer.

729
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:00,560
Give him some more water.

730
00:40:13,160 --> 00:40:14,160
Is this okay?

731
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:16,240
Yes.

732
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:17,680
Thank you.

733
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:21,080
Jiaxu, do you want some hangover soup?

734
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:22,880
I don't drink alcohol.

735
00:40:22,960 --> 00:40:23,840
I don't need it.

736
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:26,400
It's late. You should go to bed.

737
00:40:26,480 --> 00:40:28,160
I'll sleep after taking a shower.

738
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:31,000
Right, Jiaxu.

739
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:34,520
You need a towel

740
00:40:34,600 --> 00:40:36,040
and other things.

741
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:58,920
Attention, ladies and gentlemen.

742
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:00,400
Passengers traveling to Yihe

743
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:04,200
on Nanwu Airlines Flight NW413,

744
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:06,920
please proceed to Gate Eightfor boarding.

745
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:11,400
Passengers traveling to Yihe

746
00:41:11,480 --> 00:41:15,240
on Nanwu Airlines Flight NW413,

747
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:18,000
please proceed to Gate Eightfor boarding.

748
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:22,320
PROSPERITY

749
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,000
Jiaxu,

750
00:41:52,800 --> 00:41:53,760
Happy Lunar New Year.

751
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:15,120
JIAXU, HAPPY LUNAR NEW YEAR
